body:
Yeah, it's the irony of their "akshually sweaty, it's a private company so it can censor whatever it wants!" argument as opposed to their usual "make the state own everything, capitalism bad socialism good"!

I agree it's more authright but PCM never uses the quadrants correctly. For example SJWs are usually put in libleft even though they're actually as far up the authoritarian axis as possible. Libright is also misused quite a bit. In fact the only one that I think consistently gets used right is authleft.
